NOTICE OF UNPAID ASSESSMENT LIEN AGAINST PROPERTY
FOR SUMS NOT PAID TO PROPERTY OWNERS ASSOCIATION
THE STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
WHEREAS, Jeffrey Shokrian and Cristina Shokrian (referred to herein as the "Owner")
are the owners of the real property locally known as 3738 Sunset Cliff, San Antonio, Texas 78261
and legally known as Lot 21, Block 26, CIBOLO CANYON UNIT-5, PHASE 2, Bexar County,
Texas more particularly described in Volume 9572 page 97-99, of the Deed and Plat Records of
Bexar County, Texas (the "Property");
WHEREAS, the Property is subject to the Cibolo Canyons Resort Master Covenant,
recorded under Document No. 20050216763, of the Official Public Records of Bexar County,
Texas, and any amendments or supplements thereto (the "Restrictions");
WHEREAS, under the Restrictions and/or Texas law, Cibolo Canyons Resort
Community, Inc. (the "Association") has a contractual lien on the Property for unpaid
assessments and other sums owed by such Owner to the Association (the "Lien");
WHEREAS, as of the date of this Notice of Unpaid Assessment Lien, the Owner has
failed to pay to the Association sums totaling $3,434.27;
NOW THEREFORE, the Association hereby files its Notice of Unpaid Assessment Lien
against the Property, as authorized under the Declaration and/or Texas Law, and hereby gives
notice of its intent to foreclose such lien against said Property for nonpayment of the above
sums by having the Property sold to the highest bidder at the courthouse steps according to law
(subject to any superior mortgage), applying proceeds first to the above indebtedness to the
extent allowed under the Declaration and forwarding the remainder to said Owner at the
Owner's last known address.
Total Indebtedness. As of the date of this Notice of Unpaid Assessment Lien, the
amount due and owing to the Association for unpaid assessments and other sums is $3,434.27
together with attorney's fees of $250.00 plus costs, for a total unpaid amount of $3,752.79 (the
"Indebtedness"). Such amount will accrue interest and costs of collection as provided in the
Declaration until paid. Additional amounts assessed against the Property which accrue after
the date of this Notice of Unpaid Assessment Lien and which are not paid shall be
automatically added to the Lien. Moreover, the Association shall not rescind this Notice of
Unpaid Assessment Lien without full payment of the Indebtedness and attorney's fees and
recording costs incurred to date, plus any additional delinquent sums and attorney's fees
incurred hereafter and reimbursement of recording costs and attorney's fees incurred in
preparing and reviewing any necessary documents to effectively rescind this Notice of Unpaid
Assessment Lien, as authorized by the Declaration.
(Cibolo Canyons Resort Community, Inc. / Notice of Lien - Shokrian)
